ServletRequestContext: Retrieve the file size from the request. Calculate and return the length of the request content header. If a NumberFormatException occurs during the calculation, return the content length instead.
StringUdfSource-index: Find the index position of the last occurrence of a specified substring within another string. If the main string is empty, return the value INDEXNOTFOUND.
ReflectionToStringBuilder-tostring: Return the string built by this string builder.
SymbolTable-type: Add a new type entry of the given value into the type table of this symbol table. Does nothing if the type table already contains a similar type. Return the index of the type entry in the symbol table.
StringUdfSource-sub: Get a substring from the specified String avoiding exceptions.
MethodWriter: Add the elements indexed from start to end in currentFrame to Frame.
CharacterConverter: If the length of the value string is 0, the default type is returned. Otherwise, the element at the first position of the string is returned.
StringUdfSource-contain: Check whether str contains elements in searchStrArray. If yes, true is returned. If no, false is returned.
ReflectionToStringBuilder-cotoarr: If collection is null, convert collection to EMPTY_STRING_ARRAY. Otherwise, convert collection to an array of strings and return the array.
SymbolTable-addname: Add constant information generated by its name and type to the constant pool and return the index of the constant.
StringUdfSource-indexof: Return the first index of the searchStr in the given string.
ReflectionToStringBuilder-arrtoarr: Return a new array of strings converted from the elements which are not null of the given array,if the size of the array is zero,it will throw an exception.
